folder: 55th Street (East) & Sutton Place South, Manhattan, NY
text:
East 55th Street, west across Sutton Place.. The church spire shown is atop St. John the Evangelist R. C. Church. This is at the N. W. corner of First Avenue. The Peter Doelger brewery is on the north side of 55th Street, between Sutton Place and First Avenue.

February 9, 1939
No's. 1-2

P. L. Sperr
